  <compounddef id="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x3_d_image_sharpening__set_sharpness" kind="page">
    <compoundname>DOX_IADLX3DImageSharpening_SetSharpness</compoundname>
    <title>SetSharpness</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Sets the sharpness of AMD Radeon™ Image Sharpening on a GPU. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Sets the sharpness of AMD Radeon™ Image Sharpening on a GPU.</para>
<para><heading level="2">Syntax </heading>
</para>
<para><preformatted>
 <ref refid="group__enumerations_1ga9306b05f15578edbf79b649dd612b8c0" kindref="member">ADLX_RESULT</ref>    SetSharpness (adlx_int sharpness)
 </preformatted></para>
<para><heading level="2">Parameters </heading>
</para>
<para><variablelist>
<varlistentry><term></term></varlistentry>
<listitem><para><table rows="1" cols="5"><row>
<entry thead="no" class="paramidx"><para>1.</para>
</entry><entry thead="no" class="paramdir"><para>[in]</para>
</entry><entry thead="no" class="paramname"><para>sharpness</para>
</entry><entry thead="no" class="paramtype"><para>adlx_int</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>The new sharpness (in %). </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</listitem>
</variablelist>
</para>
<para><heading level="2">Return Value </heading>
</para>
<para>If the sharpness is successfully set, <bold>ADLX_OK</bold> is returned.<linebreak/>
 If the sharpness is not successfully set, an error code is returned.<linebreak/>
 Refer to <ref refid="group__enumerations_1ga9306b05f15578edbf79b649dd612b8c0" kindref="member">ADLX_RESULT</ref> for success codes and error codes.<linebreak/>
</para>
<para><heading level="2">Additional Info </heading>
</para>
<para>AMD Radeon Image Sharpening restores clarity softened by other effects to in-game visuals, and select productivity and media applications.</para>
<para><heading level="2">Requirements </heading>
</para>
<para><table rows="2" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Header</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>include &quot;I3DSettings.h&quot;</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Minimum version</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>1.0</para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
